"title": "7342: cleanliness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7342: cleanliness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Careful, fastidious attention to personal hygiene, particularly important in the climate of the Near East. In Scripture, sin is associated with lack of cleanliness, whereas redemption and baptism are linked with washing.</p>\n<h2>Cleanliness through bathing</h2>\n<h3>As part of general personal hygiene</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:1-Ruth3:3\">RUT 3:1–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:10\">JHN 13:10</a></p>\n<h3>For cleansing from uncleanness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:15-Lev17:16\">LEV 17:15–17:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:8-Lev14:9\">LEV 14:8–14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:13\">LEV 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:9-2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:9–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Cleanliness through washing feet</h2>\n<h3>A customary practice after a journey</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:1-Gen19:2\">GEN 19:1–19:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1-Gen18:5\">GEN 18:1–18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:32\">GEN 24:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:24\">GEN 43:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:40-1Sam25:42\">1SA 25:40–25:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:6-2Sam11:8\">2SA 11:6–11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36-Luke7:47\">LUK 7:36–7:47</a></p>\n<h3>As a sign of humility and love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:2-John13:17\">JHN 13:2–13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:9-1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:9–5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Cleanliness through washing clothes</h2>\n<h3>As part of general personal hygiene</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:3\">ISA 7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:17\">2KI 18:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:2\">ISA 36:2</a></p>\n<h3>For cleansing from uncleanness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:40\">LEV 11:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:10-Exod19:11\">EXO 19:10–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:14-Exod19:15\">EXO 19:14–19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:6\">LEV 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:26\">LEV 16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:7\">NUM 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:21\">NUM 19:21</a></p>\n<h2>Cleanliness through washing faces and hands</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16-Matt6:18\">MAT 6:16–6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:18-Exod30:21\">EXO 30:18–30:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:30-Exod40:31\">EXO 40:30–40:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:2\">MAT 15:2</a></p>\n<h2>Cleanliness through washing infants at birth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:4-Ezek16:5\">EZK 16:4–16:5</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Cleansing agents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:22\">JER 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:30-Job9:31\">JOB 9:30–9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:2\">MAL 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>The Pharisees' concern with outer cleanliness to the exclusion of inner purity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:1–7:23</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:1–15:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:37-Luke11:41\">LUK 11:37–11:41</a></p>\n<h2>Cleanliness used metaphorically</h2>\n<h3>Lack of cleanliness associated with sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1-Zech3:7\">ZEC 3:1–3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:4\">ISA 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:43-Matt12:45\">MAT 12:43–12:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:24-Luke11:26\">LUK 11:24–11:26</a></p>\n<h3>Cleanliness associated with righteousness and purity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:14\">REV 19:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:14\">JER 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:4–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:6\">REV 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:8\">REV 19:8</a></p>\n<h3>Baptism compared to washing away sins</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:21-1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:21–3:22</a></p>",
